title: Fantasy Football Week 7: You Play To Win The Game
itunes:title: Fantasy Football Week 7: You Play To Win The Game
description:
Do you trade Ryan "Fitzmagic?" Do you pick up Tua Tagovailoa? Will Le'Veon Bell recapture his dominance in Kansas City?


Michael Barr, Rich Trueman, and Damian Sassower reflect on all of this as they look ahead to week 7 action.


Check out Rich’s fantasy football column every Thursday on the Bloomberg Terminal.


If you listened to the podcast last week Rich made a huge pick.


Don't miss out because his moves can turn you into a fantasy champ.
